org.itsnat.comp

Interface ItsNatHTMLComponentManager

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ItsNatComponentManager

    public interface ItsNatHTMLComponentManager
extends ItsNatComponentManager
    Utility interface to manage (create, register etc) ItsNat HTML based components of the associated ItsNatDocument.
    Author:
    Jose Maria Arranz Santamaria
    See Also:
    ItsNatHTMLDocument.getItsNatHTMLComponentManager()

      • createItsNatHTMLTable

        ItsNatHTMLTable createItsNatHTMLTable(org.w3c.dom.html.HTMLTableElement element,
                                    ItsNatTableStructure structure,
                                    NameValue[] artifacts)
        Creates a new HTML table component.
        Parameters:
        element - the DOM element associated. If null a new (empty) table is created.
        structure - the specified structure, if null then is obtained from artifacts ("useStructure"), if not defined then from markup ("useStructure" attribute), if not defined the default structure is used.
        artifacts - artifacts used to construct the component. May be null.
        Returns:
        a new HTML table component.
